            <div data-seq="278836394" data-index="2" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">最省钱的门票住宿与交通攻略篇（必看）</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278836397">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;建议到了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>的小伙伴第一时间下火车就先办理一张一卡通冲值卡~&nbsp;地铁站和中信银行都可以办，办的时候交20元押金，退卡时候再还给你，不过我没退，直接拿去当纪念了！<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;五天游玩的小伙伴，建议冲值30元左右，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>交通都很便宜的，反正无论你冲多少退卡时候都会返给你，但是我没选择退卡，直接带回家当纪念了哈哈！
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278836432" data-seq="278836433" data-pid="278836432" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:580px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8169610/278836432.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:341px;width:580px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/41/D7/wKgBZ1jtkoyAJZ1nAAPOuFEo0Kk700.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/41/D7/wKgBZ1jtkoyAJZ1nAAPOuFEo0Kk700.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278836432" alt="" />
