        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8169610/278836479.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:916px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1A/92/wKgBZ1lopoCAL6hXAAL7LprHzzA75.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1A/92/wKgBZ1lopoCAL6hXAAL7LprHzzA75.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278836479" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" target="_blank" class="_j_anchor">
                    <i class="house"></i>北京
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278836490">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;住宿的话游客们肯定是住前门了~那里离天安门最近，不光看升旗方便，交通和吃饭也是最方便的~&nbsp;一开始打算住的是前门的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/24058.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="上林" target="_blank">上林</a>国际青旅，四人间床位65/人，后来订了7天连锁酒店。<br />
<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;原因很简单~&nbsp;7天的卫生和环境肯定比青旅要好，而且在淘宝可以找商家代订，比官网基础价格上还能再优惠几十块，这样算下来一个标间只要200出头（青途一个标间也要200多的）<br />
<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;所以建议以后去各地旅行的小伙伴，如果经济不是很紧张的话，可以几个人一起拼七天，直接去淘宝找人代订就好了！&nbsp;哪怕你是四个人也可以睡一个标间两张床，登记的时候登记两个人先上楼，等前面的人进房间了，后面的人再跟着上楼就没服务员管了！
        </p>
            <div data-seq="278836499" data-index="3" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
